    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just wanting a break though. it feels like there isnt even a version of the future where things get better. like no matter how much i fight, the world is just gonna stay this way and i'll just be stuck in this constant cycle of pain. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the struggle is to just... not be here anymore. does that sound crazy?",
